headline: Huntington Ingalls Ships Arleigh Burke-Class Destroyer to US Navy
summary: HII strengthens its role as a top U.S. naval contractor with the delivery of Flight III destroyer Ted Stevens, marking another milestone for Ingalls Shipbuilding.
